	-New database engine
	-Some non-popular features left
	-Running all tasks in backround
	-Own ip-up code. (Using dynamic DNS is available
	 under all distribs.)
	-Rewritten DNS selection algorhythm.
	-utf8 texts for compatibility all languages
	-Some changes in the widgets
	-More than 700 supported phones
	-New providers, upgraded data of providers
	
	Seems not too much, maybe that is, but we're feeling it fatiguing.

